  m_text: 'Long ago, beyond the reach of stars, a celestial thief fled with a sacred
    artifact stolen from a cosmic deity.

    The object pulsed with unstable power,
    bending reality around it as it traveled.

    In its desperate escape, the being
    descended toward a distant, untouched world.

    That world was known as Aetheraelis.'
